name: COMMONWEALTH of Pennsylvania, Petitioner v. James SNOOK, Respondent

parties: COMMONWEALTH of Pennsylvania, Petitioner v. James SNOOK, Respondent.

opinions.text:
ORDER
PER CURIAM.
AND NOW, this 5th day of June, 2009, the Petition for Allowance of Appeal is hereby DENIED. This Court’s Order dated May 29, 2009, granting the Commonwealth’s Emergency Application for Supersedeas is hereby VACATED.
opinions.author: PER CURIAM.
